Usage: modifyBudget [-help] -file <string> -view <string> {-ptn <string> | -inst <string>} [-setup  | -hold  ]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-file <string>          # input file containing manual budgets
                        # (string, required)
-hold                   # modify hold information (bool, optional)
-inst <string>          # hierarchical instance for which manual budgets would
                        # be applied (string, required)
-ptn <string>           # partition for which manual budgets would be applied
                        # (string, required)
-setup                  # modify setup information (bool, optional)
-view <string>          # modify budgets for a specific view only
                        # (string, required)